---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import FloatingNav from '../components/site/FloatingNav.astro';
import FooterArchive from '../components/site/FooterArchive.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Heritage | Vedic Harvest"
  description="Explore the fictional roots of Vedic Harvest and its legacy of purity since 1951."
>
  <FloatingNav />

  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <section class="py-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="rounded-[2.2rem] bg-surface px-8 py-14 md:px-14 md:py-16">
        <p class="font-body text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-clove/60">Heritage Chronicle</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 font-heading text-5xl leading-tight text-clove md:text-6xl">Our Fictional Roots, Crafted with Purpose</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl font-body text-lg leading-relaxed text-clove/78">
          Vedic Harvest was born as a fictional heritage house inspired by timeless Indian pantry traditions,
          where every ingredient is curated for purity, aroma, and trust.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-12">
        <article class="rounded-[2rem] bg-dough p-8 shadow-[0_14px_28px_rgba(62,39,35,0.08)]">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-clove">The Founding Vision</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-clove/78">
            In our fictional narrative, Vedic Harvest began in 1951 as a small family collective that believed
            true flavor starts at the source. The founders traveled farm clusters season by season,
            selecting crops for natural aroma, vibrant color, and nutritional integrity.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-clove/78">
            That philosophy shaped a strict sourcing ritual: careful lot selection, transparent handling,
            and quality-first decisions before every batch reached the pantry shelf.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="rounded-[2rem] bg-dough p-8 shadow-[0_14px_28px_rgba(62,39,35,0.08)]">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-clove">The Heritage Promise</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-clove/78">
            Today, that fictional heritage continues through modern hygiene standards and artisanal discipline.
            Vedic Harvest prioritizes ingredient authenticity, minimal processing, and consistent food safety
            so families can cook with confidence every day.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-clove/78">
            The result is a portfolio concept that feels grounded, premium, and culturally rooted,
            while remaining entirely fictional for presentation and demonstration purposes.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <FooterArchive />
</BaseLayout>
